Victoria Vinton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Victoria_Vinton 0 Victoria Vinton, born Victoria Velnette Vinton (August 23, 1912 – June 12, 1980) was an early B-movie actress, starring in over thirty films from 1932 into 1940, mostly in westerns.
